                        <interp inst="t18400511-name-320" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>WILLIAM ADAMSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a carpenter, and live in Bartholomew-close. I was working at No. 22, Hensley-street, Euston-square, on the 28th of April—I left these tools safe about half-past eight o'clock—I afterwards found them at Mr. Cubitt's—these are mine.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Had you other property there? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—I had left no one on the premises.</p>
